original_title: The Naked Brothers Band: Mystery Girl
overview: The Naked Brothers Band is making a major motion picture! But it's far from quiet on the set. Nat can't understand why Rosalina seems to be sabotaging herself with terrible acting in order to get written out of the film. Meanwhile, Alex freaks out when he discovers that his part in the movie calls for him to kiss a girl!
title: The Naked Brothers Band: Mystery Girl
